imageDescription: A collage featuring an image of Lana Del Rey in the center of the picture, wearing a white dress, with black claws. She has a silver heart necklace on, and her eyes are black. Surrounding the image are many different images, such as a butterfly, a rose, a bird, and a heart. There are also black, dripping marks all around the picture.
